    <data key="d0">Axiom SL - Automated Single Tenant SaaS Risk and Reporting Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8TExnSvZqt0</data>
    <data key="d2">Automated deployment of single-tenant application stacks using ECS and RDS/Redshift. Uses Redshift Spectrum for warm historical queries on S3, coupled with comprehensive native security services.</data>
